WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 5730 AND 5849 THEN 'BAND 17' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 5850 AND 5999 THEN 'BAND 18' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 6000 AND 6149 THEN 'BAND 19' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 6150 AND 6449 THEN 'BAND 20' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 6450 AND 6599 THEN 'BAND 21' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 6600 AND 7399 THEN 'BAND 22' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 7500 AND 7699 THEN 'BAND 23' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 7700 AND 8039 THEN 'BAND 24' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 8040 AND 8689 THEN 'BAND 25'
WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 36000 AND 36199 THEN 'BAND 33' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 36200 AND 36349 THEN 'BAND 34' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 36350 AND 36949 THEN 'BAND 35' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 36950 AND 37549 THEN 'BAND 36' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 37550 AND 37749 THEN 'BAND 37' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 37750 AND 38249 THEN 'BAND 38' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 38250 AND 38649 THEN 'BAND 39' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 38650 AND 39649 THEN 'BAND 40' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 39650 AND 41589 THEN 'BAND 41' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 41590 AND 43589 THEN 'BAND 42' WHEN LNCEL_EARFCN_DL BETWEEN 43590 AND 45589 THEN 'BAND 43' ELSE 'BAND UNKNOWN' END BAND FROM ROH_C_LTE_LNCEL WHERE CONF_ID = 1 AND VALID_FINISH_TIME > SYSDATE AND OBJECT_STATE = 1) order by 1
